                    <div class="track-step"><div class="track-step-num">2</div><div class="track-step-text"><strong>Note the Tracking ID</strong><span>Your receipt shows a code like <code style="background:#e2e8f0;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">TRK-XXXXXXXX</code>.</span></div></div>
